Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.96,0:00:25.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多麼動聽的歌聲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.30,0:00:37.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汝想活下去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.47,0:00:41.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.77,0:00:43.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還不想死
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.23,0:00:47.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何祈禱著不願死去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.27,0:00:52.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹妹… 我有個妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.82,0:00:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然孩提時分開後 再未相見
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.12,0:00:59.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會去迎接 我唯一的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.20,0:01:02.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明那樣發誓了的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.75,0:01:10.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我卻至今沒能實現那個誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.01,0:01:13.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.68,0:01:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要活著 伴她左右
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.48,0:01:25.02,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Shadow wish go to
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.48,0:01:25.02,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Shadow wish go to
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.02,0:01:28.42,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}It's me. Is that so pretty
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.02,0:01:28.42,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}It's me. Is that so pretty
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.42,0:01:32.89,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}You cann't choose my fate
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.42,0:01:32.89,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}You cann't choose my fate
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.80,0:01:39.20,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}乾いた風に抱かれて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.80,0:01:39.20,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}迎面吹著乾燥的風
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.20,0:01:45.67,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}生命への 真偽を覚え 刻む想い
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.20,0:01:45.67,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}懂得了生命的真偽 銘刻於心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.67,0:01:49.08,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}ただ 傍に居たいと願い
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.67,0:01:49.08,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只是 祈願待在你身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.08,0:01:51.65,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}人を愛し 人を憎み
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.08,0:01:51.65,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}愛過 恨過
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.65,0:01:55.15,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}悲しさは  優しさ生む
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.65,0:01:55.15,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}悲傷最後化作溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.15,0:02:00.12,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}例え光が 消えたとしても
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.15,0:02:00.12,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就算陷入無盡黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.12,0:02:04.89,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明日の希望を探すよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.12,0:02:04.89,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}仍會尋覓明日希望
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.89,0:02:09.20,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}燃えた血の呼吸 消え寄せれば
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.89,0:02:09.20,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}燃燒的血液 停止了呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.20,0:02:14.27,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因果は奇跡に変わる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.20,0:02:14.27,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因果之緣 最終轉化成奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.27,0:02:16.47,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}So so so wonderland
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.27,0:02:16.47,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}So so so wonderland
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.47,0:02:18.94,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Shadow wish go to
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.47,0:02:18.94,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Shadow wish go to
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.94,0:02:22.68,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}闇を搔き分け
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.94,0:02:22.68,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}撥開黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.68,0:02:26.51,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}手を伸ばすよ どこまでも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.68,0:02:26.51,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}伸手向前 追尋你到任何地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.51,0:02:28.78,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}It's the worst key
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.51,0:02:28.78,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}It's the worst key
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.78,0:02:32.42,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}いつか 変えるまで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.78,0:02:32.42,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}總有一天 命運將會轉變
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.42,0:02:37.09,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}涙の意味 無駄にはしない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.42,0:02:37.09,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不要讓眼淚白流
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.09,0:02:41.73,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}螺旋のように 蠢く果てに
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.09,0:02:41.73,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如螺旋一般交織騷動的盡頭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.73,0:02:44.73,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(0,400)}吠えて 交わる FATE
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.73,0:02:44.73,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(0,400)}狂吠吧 交織的命運
