Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.04,0:03:06.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信乃 上車吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.95,0:03:08.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 掰掰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.58,0:03:12.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥 你要去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.84,0:03:14.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要和信乃一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.63,0:03:19.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了不行 我們的座位在二等席
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.60,0:03:34.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 可以跟您同坐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.65,0:03:36.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 沒關係請坐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.98,0:03:38.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.33,0:03:47.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信乃請去窗邊坐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.04,0:03:53.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是黃昏時分抵達帝都 不妨睡一覺哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.17,0:03:55.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.13,0:04:00.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩位都是教會的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.63,0:04:01.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是兄弟嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.68,0:04:04.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 算是那一類的關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.97,0:04:08.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以教會的水準來說還真是好福利啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.93,0:04:10.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡可是一等車廂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.14,0:04:13.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說一向如此呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.23,0:04:17.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我一個人時無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.53,0:04:19.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是因為帶著孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.90,0:04:22.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到帝都也有很長的路途
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.11,0:04:23.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莊介
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.78,0:04:24.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.95,0:04:27.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面雨下得好大
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.16,0:04:33.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢 什麼時候下起來的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.21,0:04:33.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.21,0:04:38.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乘務員剛才通知說暴風雨來襲了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.13,0:04:42.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能這樣順利開往帝都就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.93,0:04:44.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暴風雨是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.43,0:04:46.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明剛才還萬里晴空呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.89,0:04:51.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信乃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.73,0:04:55.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為下雨嗎 著涼了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.19,0:04:57.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.27,0:05:02.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這就去餐車 拿些熱飲料
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.03,0:05:07.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是位保護過度的哥哥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.58,0:05:11.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說是你把他支開了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.25,0:05:13.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.42,0:05:16.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感受到雪的氣息了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.00,0:05:21.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.05,0:05:24.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟突然間說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.93,0:05:29.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這雨說不定會出人意料的變成雪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.85,0:05:33.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那不可能的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.52,0:05:36.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在不是那種季節吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.52,0:05:38.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 正常情況下是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.44,0:05:42.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊 真想看一看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.48,0:05:45.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盛夏降臨的白雪 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.70,0:05:53.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下雪了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.54,0:05:54.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.42,0:06:05.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真幸運！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.81,0:06:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.40,0:06:23.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼…這不是還有位置嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.53,0:06:27.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個列車員竟敢騙我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.86,0:06:31.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 小鬼 坐到那邊去！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.83,0:06:38.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 有位子不讓顧客做 安得什麼心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.17,0:06:42.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…列車員沒有騙你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.84,0:06:44.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是一等席
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.96,0:06:48.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你這樣的人本來都不應該進入的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.39,0:06:50.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.30,0:06:53.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你拽什麼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.51,0:06:56.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因為有你這樣的人！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.27,0:07:00.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃我一記眼球
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.57,0:07:16.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個混…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.00,0:07:20.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那老老實實待著
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.71,0:07:21.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹得漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.83,0:07:25.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼…眼球？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.17,0:07:25.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信乃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.05,0:07:27.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝奶茶好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.63,0:07:28.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.05,0:07:33.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白雪又變回雨水了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.55,0:07:36.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然會下八月雪 真是太稀奇了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.02,0:07:37.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.18,0:07:40.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼球…這裡有個眼球…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.10,0:07:43.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼眼球啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.87,0:07:53.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睦月…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.62,0:07:58.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睦月
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.21,0:08:00.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天我一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.92,0:08:04.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,濱路？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.88,0:08:07.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,濱路哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.17,0:08:10.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輪到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.26,0:08:13.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天狐想快點丟鬼牌 已經等不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.14,0:08:15.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心虛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.14,0:08:16.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 濱路？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.39,0:08:18.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,濱路路
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.93,0:08:23.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受不了了…不要隨隨便便一直叫人家的名字！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.69,0:08:30.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起…是我失敬了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.36,0:08:36.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…已經很久沒想起過了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.24,0:08:38.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣焦躁的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.50,0:08:40.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睦月
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.50,0:08:42.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睦月…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.13,0:08:47.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.67,0:08:51.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 沒注意聽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.38,0:08:52.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真過分呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.22,0:08:57.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心 再過不久小信他們就會回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.60,0:09:01.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.90,0:09:08.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是愛睡覺的孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.28,0:09:12.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為今天早上很早就叫他起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.24,0:09:16.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且本來小孩子就很能睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.37,0:09:18.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的如此嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.41,0:09:20.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.16,0:09:23.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪居然會聽這個孩子的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.00,0:09:29.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而這個男子…明明與我同處一室
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.17,0:09:30.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼沒有任何感覺？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.89,0:09:37.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該很冷吧…正常來說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.05,0:09:40.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.69,0:09:46.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個神秘詭異的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.06,0:09:49.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經縮小不少了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.69,0:09:53.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變小了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.36,0:09:56.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是被信乃找到會真的把你丟掉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.62,0:10:00.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這幫人到底是什麼人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.67,0:10:15.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聞到了 聞到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.76,0:10:18.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡面飄散著妖怪的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.59,0:10:20.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裡呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.18,0:10:24.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖怪居然也與人類一同乘車
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.35,0:10:29.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 時代真是變了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.03,0:10:36.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是八月盛夏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.15,0:10:38.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡卻寒冷逼人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.49,0:10:42.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼珠…眼珠！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.37,0:10:47.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這醉鬼 睡在這裡你會凍死的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.42,0:10:52.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.34,0:11:01.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖怪躲在這裡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.35,0:11:04.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本中大和尚來收拾你們了！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.27,0:11:11.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三個人？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.77,0:11:14.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到竟是化成人形的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.95,0:11:27.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現出原形了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.50,0:11:32.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.93,0:11:41.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.02,0:12:02.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.36,0:12:05.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪姬？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.84,0:12:24.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是你 雪姬！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.46,0:12:25.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.01,0:12:29.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.47,0:12:34.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼摸得到她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.56,0:12:37.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個認識！？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.23,0:12:41.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一次下雪天在森林裡遇難了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.27,0:12:42.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還好被雪姬救了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.11,0:12:46.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後每年冬天 我們經常在一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.07,0:12:49.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎…大雪天遇到危險？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.53,0:12:52.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是頭一次聽到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.20,0:12:55.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪姬 在這裡遇到你真是嚇我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.53,0:12:57.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森林神也會擔心你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.79,0:12:59.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說最近怎麼都沒看到你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.87,0:13:01.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.09,0:13:14.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是和他在一起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.14,0:13:20.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧…既然這樣我就長話短說了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.27,0:13:24.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何都要拜託你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.77,0:13:27.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能勸她放了我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.11,0:13:29.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.40,0:13:31.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經受不了了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.24,0:13:34.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從她纏上我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.40,0:13:33.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}讓你久等啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.45,0:13:38.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的朋友和情人都因為討厭而離我遠去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.16,0:13:42.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬天也就算了 連夏天我的身邊也是冷颼颼的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.50,0:13:45.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然身體覺得冷 但是心更冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.67,0:13:48.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我受不了這樣的生活了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.92,0:13:50.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我愛莫能助
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.59,0:13:51.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.63,0:13:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪姬不會在這個季節出現在人前
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.64,0:13:59.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可見她是想保護你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.60,0:14:02.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 如果雪女離開你…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.60,0:14:04.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就沒命了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.98,0:14:12.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定是在大雪天中瀕死時被她所救吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.44,0:14:13.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.57,0:14:17.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道我一輩子都要這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.45,0:14:20.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要認為只有你如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.37,0:14:25.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了救你 雪姬可是付出了相等的代價
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.00,0:14:29.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖怪為了救你這樣的普通人類…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.96,0:14:33.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少她也…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.90,0:14:53.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信乃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.19,0:14:58.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走過這座橋 就快抵達帝都了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.41,0:15:08.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 該拿這位大師怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.67,0:15:10.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管他的 就放在那吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.92,0:15:14.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼珠…眼珠…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.31,0:15:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事的 姬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.81,0:15:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經習慣寒冷了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.73,0:15:32.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪姬救了我一命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.69,0:15:34.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.41,0:15:42.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 你不去送送他們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.83,0:15:45.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得遇到了久違的朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.29,0:15:50.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很少見啊 雪姬還有人類的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.71,0:15:56.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了 忘記問他們名字了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.47,0:16:01.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 前面的兩個人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.14,0:16:05.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大個子和小個子 請等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.52,0:16:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大個子？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.68,0:16:07.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小個子？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.56,0:16:13.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫道節 犬山道節
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.40,0:16:14.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.57,0:16:17.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬川莊介
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.07,0:16:19.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬塚信乃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.16,0:16:22.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那再會了 雪姬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.66,0:16:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有道節
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.37,0:16:26.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接叫我的名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.45,0:16:30.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村雨說 它也向和你打個招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.79,0:16:33.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.80,0:16:39.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保重啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.47,0:16:43.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烏鴉從手臂裡…烏鴉從手臂裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.77,0:16:54.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信乃 雪姬為救他付出了什麼代價？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.24,0:17:03.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她以前擁有十分動聽的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.95,0:17:06.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是在唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.20,0:17:10.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜歡聽了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.62,0:17:14.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能在飄雪的季節才能聽到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.50,0:17:16.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如搖籃曲一般
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.22,0:17:23.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而現在已經聽不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.36,0:18:22.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多麼動聽的歌聲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.30,0:18:44.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汝想活下去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.64,0:18:48.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.72,0:18:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還不想死
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.02,0:18:54.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何祈禱著不願死去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.64,0:18:57.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有個妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.81,0:19:02.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然孩提時分開後 再未相見
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.32,0:19:05.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我唯一的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.07,0:19:13.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她雖不如你美 但也可愛至極
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.33,0:19:15.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為她是我唯一的妹妹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.96,0:19:23.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我與幼小的她訂下了一個約定
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.71,0:19:25.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到現在都還能沒兌現
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.76,0:19:28.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便我是個不稱職的兄長
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.60,0:19:32.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我好想看看已長大了的她現在的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.77,0:19:34.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後去接她
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.60,0:19:37.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向她道歉 告訴她「對不起我來晚了」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.35,0:19:38.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.86,0:19:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想活下去 回到她的身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.78,0:19:57.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汝跟妾身唯一的朋友說了同樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.92,0:20:01.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就由妾身來拯救汝之命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.38,0:20:27.05,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}残像 we flash back する
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.38,0:20:27.05,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}殘像 we flash back
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.12,0:20:35.13,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}慟哭の先に　未来を沸かす光
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.12,0:20:35.13,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}慟哭之前 沸騰著未來的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.13,0:20:40.57,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}選んだ空が　示した夜明け
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.13,0:20:40.57,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}選擇的那片天空 昭示著拂曉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.57,0:20:45.84,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}生きる意味を知るために
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.57,0:20:45.84,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}想要探尋生存的意義
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.84,0:20:51.24,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}打たれてなお輝く輪数があるなら
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.84,0:20:51.24,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}反覆捶打 光輝的明日若是存在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.24,0:20:54.15,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}この身くらい迷わず
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.24,0:20:54.15,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我絲毫不會迷茫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.18,0:20:56.28,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}差し出せばいい
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.18,0:20:56.28,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}挺身而出
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.28,0:21:01.72,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今　果てしき風の向こうへ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.28,0:21:01.72,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}現在 奔向勁風的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.72,0:21:07.23,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}いつか世界が溶けて消えても
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.72,0:21:07.23,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}即使世界總有消融的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.23,0:21:12.70,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}辛いだけが　掴んた絆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.23,0:21:12.70,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雖然艱辛 也要緊緊地握住羈絆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.70,0:21:18.17,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}決して解けない　より強く
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.70,0:21:18.17,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}暗暗加力 絕不鬆開
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.17,0:21:24.21,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(0,290)}運命を結ぶ　String of pain
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.17,0:21:24.21,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(0,290)}連結著命運的 String of pain
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.27,0:21:42.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別猶豫了 你們也進來吃飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.90,0:21:44.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.31,0:21:45.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給您添麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.61,0:21:48.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回來了 浪蕩兒子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.94,0:21:49.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.94,0:21:53.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人們在裡面吃飯呢   快去給我幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.41,0:21:54.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.45,0:21:57.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常歡迎你們能來玩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.53,0:22:00.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚吃火鍋  你們可要放開了吃
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.83,0:22:02.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火鍋？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.21,0:22:04.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.83,0:22:05.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛野先生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.88,0:22:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.04,0:22:10.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨古那屋
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.17,0:22:13.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來你是這家店的店小二啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.13,0:22:16.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  我是這裡老闆娘的兒子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.14,0:22:17.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兒子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.72,0:22:21.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們暫時要在帝都住一段時間
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.56,0:22:22.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你們多多照顧了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.65,0:22:26.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  你們都在…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.27,0:22:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肉肉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.07,0:22:30.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要開動啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.98,0:22:33.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村雨  那塊肉是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.11,0:22:35.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信乃  肉的話這邊也有
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.28,0:22:36.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旦開野  你的袖子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.57,0:22:38.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好險呀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.87,0:22:41.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信乃  這塊肉也給你吃
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.58,0:22:46.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.00,0:22:49.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是  那可真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.63,0:22:55.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  我煮好的肉怎麼沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.76,0:22:57.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到自己鍋裡煮去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.05,0:23:01.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這陣子好多「人」都聚集在了一起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.14,0:22:59.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}好好吃 好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.68,0:23:01.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}這塊肉是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.64,0:23:04.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}好吃好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.89,0:23:03.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全聚到那個孩子身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.98,0:23:08.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像是被磁鐵吸引在一起一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.77,0:23:10.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真真切切…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.37,0:23:22.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們竟敢還不回來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.95,0:23:24.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟我說也…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.00,0:23:27.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…所以說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.25,0:23:29.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有家人 也找不到妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.59,0:23:32.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連個戀人都木有讓我的人生靠啥維持下去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.59,0:23:33.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不這麼覺得嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.38,0:23:34.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.17,0:23:36.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明明還年輕是不是太老氣橫秋了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.68,0:23:39.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在很想揍人
